description: When hot summer nights give way to misty fall mornings, effortlessly slide into Nana Hele, a sneaker-meets-slipper mid-cut boot with comfortable shearling lining in the forefoot, a pebbled waterproof leather upper, and their 'Wet Grip Rubber' outsole to keep the warmth in and the weather out.
name: Olukai Nana Hele - Mens
